snippet.textDisplay:
I knew this one would be special. The more I listen to it, the more I love it. I have adored Hanan's vocals since I started listening to him. And Kaavish, I think the comments on here are enough, what more can you say about them. They are a feeling that you can't put in words, one that you know is true and that reverbates through your soul.

Probably my favourite of the season so far. I just wish that it was longer. It ends too soon, and you feel like that the song didn't say all it needed to. The humming at the end would hit a lot more if there was more build-up to it, it needed more time.

Edit: Also Gumby is back!! Gumby and Kaavish is one video, what more can you ask for.
